id artery of a healthy human\nsubject and gave a PWV and patterns of wave intensity that were consistent with\nearlier measurements. The new system may have clinical utility, for example in\nscreening for, and monitoring of, heart failure.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 29 May 2022 18:01:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-31"}
